Installation:

  % gzip -cd aeinfo-@AEINFO_VERSION@.tar.gz | tar xvf -  # unpack the sources
  % cd aeinfo-@AEINFO_VERSION@                           # change to the toplevel directory
  % make                                    # build
  [ Become root if necessary ]
  % make install                            # install the binary    

Have fun with this software (try 'aeinfo help')
